{"tid":2249620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日lunchtime去左Donki買野，點知臨放工收到大信封","createTime":"2020-10-19T12:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T14:47:15.000Z","uid":340192,"like":28,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ab5bc9d85a30d0c53462e673bc7aabc726270bbe","tid":2249620,"uid":340192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:36:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小妹中五畢業，依家係間外資公司做文員。<br />\n最近公司空降左個鬼佬經理黎香港，今日臨收工比HR叫左入房話我已經被解僱，一直做得好地地，完全唔明點解會咁，希望大家評下理。<br />\n<br />\n今日lunchtime食完飯，見仲有時間剩就去左公司樓下Donki買左好大袋零食做下午茶。<br />\n<br />\n買完翻到office，撞到鬼佬老細，佢手指指住我個Donki膠袋，笑笑口咁用英文問我野，不過我本身英文麻麻地，其唔係太明佢講乜。但畢竟第一次傾計，盡量都想同佢好好溝通打好關係。<br />\n<br />\n咁我估佢都係對我袋Donki零食有興趣，咁我咪用英文講「你睇黎真係好鍾意Donki」， &ldquo;You really look like Donki&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n點知鬼佬老細當堂由笑笑口變到冇哂表情，我果下呆左唔識比反應，唯有唱下Donki歌緩和氣氛，Don Don Don Donki, Don Don Donki~<br />\n<br />\n點知鬼佬老細面都黑哂，氣沖沖咁入左HR房唔知講左乜，傾左好耐都冇出黎，結果我臨放工就收到HR大信封。<br />\n<br />\n依家又難搵工，都唔知點算好。唉d鬼佬上司真係好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c219d443ba0dc72ee218302815aa01284e288742","tid":2249620,"uid":44569,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:39:33.000Z","msg":"1 分比是咁的"},{"pid":"433a40486c70ce4d5f76e1ece7e96444b5f190a4","tid":2249620,"uid":38904,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ifunny.co/images/5e9773e303899c535b0c2535a7a8a3bda9d75eed6d769aad16e8188056925d8e_1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ifunny.co%2Fimages%2F5e9773e303899c535b0c2535a7a8a3bda9d75eed6d769aad16e8188056925d8e_1.gif&h=b314adb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb0b6c8e66896959313b3ee2e37e5f24419ba264","tid":2249620,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm